rows.label: qst202003_msg0001
rows.name:
So you've come to get firewood 
in place of Musubi-san?

rows.label: qst202003_msg0002
rows.name:
That's too bad. I won't be 
able to meet Musubi-san today.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0004
rows.name: Ah, sorry. It's just a joke.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0005
rows.name:
The firewood is in 
the scrap wood area, so take 
as much as you like.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0006
rows.name: By the way, is old man Dofusay doing well?

rows.label: qst202003_msg0008
rows.name:
I was really taken care 
of by old man Dofusei 
and the others in the past.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0009
rows.name:
He's Superbian, himself, but he moved
here to Torigo of his own accord.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0010
rows.name: Until recently, he was teaching Gulan Drivers.

rows.label: qst202003_msg0011
rows.name:
But it seems his legs and back 
reached their limit, 
so he retired...

rows.label: qst202003_msg0012
rows.name:
Anyway, I'd better let you go. Best
not keep Musubi waiting, eh?
